description: As we move into the cooler months of the year, we are slowing our truck schedule accordingly.  If we’ll be out on the streets of St. Paul we’ll be sure to announce our plans several days in advance.The 128 Cafe is serving up delicious sandwiches, salads, burgers, and more to the streets of St. Paul. From Pork Belly Bulgogi to a "Bunyan Burger" with mushroom and blue cheese, these upscale eats are sure to blow you away at the first bite! So stop by for a taste today!
name: 128 Cafe
